---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Kuri | Raw Food, Grooming, Walking, Training and Small Doggy Daycare Christchurch"
  description="Kuri helps Christchurch dogs with raw food, grooming, walking, training and small doggy daycare from 473 Saint Asaph Street."
>
  <Header />
  <Hero
    eyebrow="Christchurch dog services"
    title="Raw food, grooming, walking, training and small doggy daycare"
    text="Kuri helps dogs eat well, look good and get the right everyday support. Our grooming, walking, training and raw food are for dogs of all sizes, while daycare is just for small dogs."
    primaryLabel="Shop Raw Food"
    primaryHref="https://shop.kuri.co.nz/"
    secondaryLabel="Book a Service"
    secondaryHref="https://kuri.portal.gingrapp.com/"
    note="473 Saint Asaph Street, Christchurch. A local team for dog food, grooming, walking, training and small-dog-only daycare."
  />
  <main>
    <section class="proof-strip" aria-label="What Kuri offers">
      <div class="wrap proof-grid">
        <div class="proof-item">
          <strong>Raw Food</strong>
          <span>Raw meals and feeding support for dogs of all sizes.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="proof-item">
          <strong>Grooming</strong>
          <span>Full grooms, bath and tidy services, and coat care for dogs of all sizes.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="proof-item">
          <strong>Small Doggy Daycare</strong>
          <span>A small-dog-only daycare environment in Christchurch.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="proof-item">
          <strong>Dog Walking</strong>
          <span>Local walks for dogs who need regular exercise and company.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="proof-item">
          <strong>Dog Training</strong>
          <span>Practical training support for better everyday behaviour.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="wrap section-head">
        <h2>Choose the part of Kuri you need</h2>
        <p class="lead">Shop raw food, book a groom, organise a walk, ask about training, or explore our small-dog-only daycare. Kuri brings the main parts of everyday dog life together in one Christchurch team.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-grid">
        <article class="service-card featured">
          <span class="service-kicker">Most direct revenue path</span>
          <h3>Raw Dog Food</h3>
          <p>Frozen, pre-portioned raw food with local guidance and a straightforward path into the shop.</p>
          <a class="button" href="https://shop.kuri.co.nz/">Shop Raw Food</a>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card">
          <h3>Dog Grooming</h3>
          <p>Calm, practical grooming in Christchurch for dogs of all sizes, including full grooms for dogs who need more than a wash.</p>
          <a class="button ghost" href="/dog-grooming-christchurch/">View Grooming</a>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card">
          <h3>Small Doggy Daycare</h3>
          <p>A small-dog-only daycare environment for owners who want a calmer, more appropriate group setting.</p>
          <a class="button ghost" href="/christchurchs-exclusive-small-doggy-daycare/">Explore Daycare</a>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card">
          <h3>Dog Walking</h3>
          <p>Local dog walking for dogs who need exercise, company and a reliable routine during the week.</p>
          <a class="button ghost" href="/dog-walking/">View Walking</a>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card">
          <h3>Dog Training</h3>
          <p>Practical training support for everyday behaviour, confidence and better communication with your dog.</p>
          <a class="button ghost" href="/kuri-dog-training/">View Training</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section soft">
      <div class="wrap split">
        <div>
          <div class="section-head">
            <h2>Kuri should feel broader than one service</h2>
            <p class="lead">The site needs to communicate that Kuri does a lot for dogs without becoming vague. The balance here is simple: lead with real food commercially, but show the services with equal clarity and confidence.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="belief-list">
            <div>
              <h3>Food matters</h3>
              <p>Raw food is a major part of the business and should stay highly visible throughout the site.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Services matter too</h3>
              <p>Grooming, walking and training are for dogs of all sizes, while Small Doggy Daycare is a small-dog-only offer.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Small dogs matter</h3>
              <p>Kuri's local difference is strongest when it speaks clearly to owners who want thoughtful care for smaller dogs.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="feature-panel">
          <span class="panel-kicker">Why people stay with Kuri</span>
          <h3>One local team, multiple ways to help</h3>
          <p>Owners can buy better food, book a groom, organise a walk, ask about training or join small-dog-only daycare without feeling like they are dealing with separate businesses.</p>
          <a class="button light" href="/about-us/">About Kuri</a>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="wrap split reverse">
        <div class="image-panel">
          <img src="/images/grooming-hero.webp" alt="A freshly groomed small dog standing calmly on a grooming table at Kuri." loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="section-head">
            <h2>Raw food gets the commercial spotlight</h2>
            <p class="lead">This section exists to support the strongest money pathway without letting the whole homepage collapse into a shop front.</p>
          </div>
          <p>Kuri raw food should be easy to understand: real ingredients, practical feeding, easier ordering, and a clear route into the shop. That matters commercially, and it also strengthens the trust story for the rest of the business.</p>
          <div class="cta-row">
            <a class="button" href="/raw-dog-food/">Learn About Raw Food</a>
            <a class="button outline-dark" href="https://shop.kuri.co.nz/">Go to Shop</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section reviews-section">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-head center">
          <h2>The homepage should send people somewhere useful</h2>
          <p class="lead">This is the working homepage pattern: broad enough to explain Kuri, direct enough to move people toward shopping, booking, calling or learning more.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="review-grid">
          <article class="review-card">
            <h3>For shoppers</h3>
            <p>Lead them toward raw food with enough trust and clarity that the shop feels like the natural next click.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="review-card">
            <h3>For service seekers</h3>
            <p>Make grooming, walking, training and Small Doggy Daycare easy to find, with clear booking pathways from the homepage.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="review-card">
            <h3>For first-time visitors</h3>
            <p>Make it obvious that Kuri is a Christchurch dog-care brand, not just a product site and not just one service.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .proof-strip {
    background: var(--kuri-red);
    color: var(--kuri-white);
  }

  .proof-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: rgb(255 255 255 / 18%);
  }

  .proof-item {
    min-height: 156px;
    padding: 22px;
    background: var(--kuri-red);
  }

  .proof-item strong,
  .service-kicker,
  .panel-kicker {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .proof-item span {
    color: rgb(255 255 255 / 82%);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
  }

  .service-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(270px, 0.95fr) repeat(2, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .service-card,
  .review-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 100%;
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--kuri-line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--kuri-white);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgb(0 0 0 / 5%);
  }

  .service-card.featured {
    grid-row: span 2;
    background: var(--kuri-light);
    border-color: var(--kuri-red);
  }

  .service-card p,
  .review-card p,
  .belief-list p,
  .feature-panel p {
    color: var(--kuri-grey);
  }

  .service-card .button,
  .feature-panel .button {
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .button.ghost,
  .button.outline-dark {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--kuri-red);
    border-color: var(--kuri-red);
  }

  .button.outline-dark {
    color: var(--kuri-ink);
    border-color: var(--kuri-ink);
  }

  .dual-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 8px;
  }

  .text-link {
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--kuri-red);
  }

  .split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(320px, 0.9fr);
    gap: 34px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .split.reverse {
    grid-template-columns: minmax(320px, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
  }

  .belief-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .feature-panel {
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--kuri-charcoal);
    color: var(--kuri-white);
  }

  .image-panel img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 22px;
  }

  .reviews-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--kuri-light) 0%, var(--kuri-white) 100%);
  }

  .review-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .service-grid,
    .review-grid,
    .split,
    .split.reverse {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .proof-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(150px, 1fr));
      overflow-x: auto;
    }

    .service-card.featured {
      grid-row: auto;
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }

    .split.reverse > :first-child {
      order: 2;
    }

    .split.reverse > :last-child {
      order: 1;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .service-grid,
    .review-grid,
    .split,
    .split.reverse {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .proof-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      overflow-x: visible;
    }

    .service-card.featured {
      grid-column: auto;
    }

    .proof-grid {
      gap: 0;
    }

    .proof-item {
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(255 255 255 / 16%);
    }

    .cta-row,
    .dual-links {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
